COAL LAND RESTORATION, UTAH NO. 50
By virtue of and pursuant to the authority vested in me by the act of June 25, 1910 (ch. 421, 36 Stat. 847), the Executive order of July 7, 1910, creating Coal Land Withdrawal, Utah No. 1, is hereby revoked as to the following-described lands:
